Global Spiral Welded Steel Pipes Market Insights
Spiral Welded Steel Pipes Market size was valued at USD 15.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 23.6 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Spiral Welded Steel Pipes Market Overview
The global Spiral Welded Steel Pipes Market is valued at USD 35.4 billion in 2024 and is projected to reach USD 56.7 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.1% during the forecast period. The market's growth is driven by increasing demand from industries such as oil & gas, construction, and water distribution, along with the need for advanced infrastructure projects. Spiral welded steel pipes are known for their high durability, corrosion resistance, and cost-effectiveness, making them ideal for applications across various sectors. As the infrastructure development across emerging economies intensifies, the market is expected to witness significant expansion in the coming years.

